\s1 About Timothy  
\p
\v 19 \w Now|strong="G1161"\w* \w I|strong="G2504"\w* \w hope|strong="G1679"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w Lord|strong="G2962"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w to|strong="G2443"\w* \w send|strong="G3992"\w* \w Timothy|strong="G5095"\w* \w to|strong="G2443"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w soon|strong="G5030"\w*, \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w I|strong="G2504"\w* \w also|strong="G2504"\w* \w may|strong="G2443"\w* \w be|strong="G2443"\w* \w encouraged|strong="G2174"\w* \w when|strong="G1161"\w* \w I|strong="G2504"\w* \w know|strong="G1097"\w* \w how|strong="G1161"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w are|strong="G3588"\w* doing.  
\v 20 \w For|strong="G1063"\w* \w I|strong="G1063"\w* \w have|strong="G2192"\w* \w no|strong="G3762"\w* \w one|strong="G3762"\w* else like-minded, \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w will|strong="G3748"\w* \w be|strong="G3588"\w* \w genuinely|strong="G1104"\w* \w concerned|strong="G3309"\w* \w about|strong="G4012"\w* \w your|strong="G2192"\w* \w welfare|strong="G3588"\w*\f + \fr 2:20 \ft This statement puzzles me; wouldn't Epaphroditus qualify? Perhaps Paul had in mind a messenger who would return with news, since Epaphroditus would stay there.\f*  
\v 21 (\w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w seek|strong="G2212"\w* \w their|strong="G1438"\w* \w own|strong="G1438"\w* interests, \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w those|strong="G3588"\w* \w of|strong="G2424"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w*).\f + \fr 2:21 \ft Unfortunately, things have not changed much in 2,000 years.\f*  
\v 22 \w But|strong="G1161"\w* \w you|strong="G3754"\w* \w know|strong="G1097"\w* \w the|strong="G1519"\w* \w proof|strong="G1382"\w* \w of|strong="G3962"\w* \w him|strong="G3588"\w*, \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w as|strong="G5613"\w* \w a|strong="G5613"\w* \w son|strong="G5043"\w* \w with|strong="G4862"\w* \w his|strong="G1519"\w* \w father|strong="G3962"\w* \w he|strong="G1161"\w* slaved\f + \fr 2:22 \ft That is what the Text says.\f* \w with|strong="G4862"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w* \w for|strong="G3754"\w* \w the|strong="G1519"\w* \w Gospel|strong="G2098"\w*.  
