\v 24 \w Still|strong="G2064"\w*, \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w am|strong="G2532"\w* \w confident|strong="G3982"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w Lord|strong="G2962"\w* \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* myself \w will|strong="G2532"\w* \w come|strong="G2064"\w* \w soon|strong="G5030"\w*.\f + \fr 2:24 \ft Recall that Paul was writing from prison.\f*   
\s1 About Epaphroditus  
\p
